born : rowan atkinson , english comedian and actor , in consett died : yevgeny tarle , 80 , soviet historian   january 7 , 1955 ( friday ) marian anderson becomes the first african - american to perform with the metropolitan opera in new york , when she sings the role of ulrica in giuseppe verdi 's un ballo in maschera ( opposite zinka milanov , then herva nelli , as amelia ) at the invitation of director rudolf bing .

